      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a ride that honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolute pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a smudge anywhere! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, babied since day one, and kept tucked away in the garage. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh car smell. I\u2019m so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
