      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a concours-level specimen featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. The powerplant retains its factory-spec tolerances, breathing through eight individual throttle bodies with a surgical 8,400 RPM redline. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission offers short, precise throws, coupled with a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) that provides telepathic feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Mechanically flawless, the subframe, rod bearings, and throttle actuators have been fastidiously monitored. This is an investment-grade masterpiece of atmospheric engineering.",
