      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements since day one. The factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections, and has been protected with a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent lingers. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by certified specialists. Every button, switch, and feature functions with factory precision. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example for the most discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
